text: Santa Cruz (Tubajon) (not to be confused with Santa Cruz, (San Jose), is one of 9 Barangays of the municipality of Tubajon, Dinagat Islands, Philippines. The barangay is northwest of the town proper of Tubajon, in the northern portion of the province.Santa Cruz, Dinagat Islands - Google Maps == References == == External links == * Province of Dinagat Islands - Official webpage Category:Philippines geography stubs Category:Barangays of Dinagat Islands
